divs: Sighting DetailsTurning on the streed where I live, (Harvest Green) I noticed in the corner of my eye a black oval moving up and down in the distance, I pulled out the camera thinking it was a plane. However the object did not have visible wings. My daughter thought it was a bird but then it changed directions and zipped over to a different spot in the sky then after a zig-zag it proceeded to act similar to a plane flying slow and controlled until out of sight. Approximate 40 seconds of video taken.
